{"tid":920244,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"立法會議員朱凱廸DQ停不了　政治審查清剿陸續來（香港這一天）","createTime":"2018-11-28T16:20:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T05:01:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"038514b861185c80482bb66d10c9250d6eecf32a","tid":920244,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T16:20:49.000Z","msg":"立法會議員朱凱廸DQ停不了　政治審查清剿陸續來（香港這一天）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Pl7aVkNho8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4Pl7aVkNho8&d=kutybnP%2Bhnz1IsuyswY%2FO57TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=6f3a0393\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4Pl7aVkNho8</a><br />\n<br />\n眾新聞<br />\n<br />\n立法會議員朱凱廸參加元朗八鄉元崗新村居民代表選舉，面臨被DQ命運；選舉主任對他昨日就港獨立場問題的答案不收貨，要求他晚上8時前再答，答中才能過提名關。楊健興分析新一輪DQ，歡迎各位發表看法。<br />\n<br />\n28-November-2018"},{"pid":"b9cbce35140d702b149b8eb9da1666676a6529c2","tid":920244,"uid":164590,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T21:51:03.000Z","msg":"快撚啲返去立法會露宿啦死乞兒"},{"pid":"30e74c8affe3e2b873814ad9889cafc0d62fadf9","tid":920244,"uid":186882,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T23:26:01.000Z","msg":"政府呢招好撚狗， 但係又好撚work<br />\n<br />\n嗱， 票王丫嘛， 你係唔係撐港獨？<br />\n<br />\n佢答係， 政府就即刻dq你， 睇死你班死泛民唔識反抗。 <br />\n<br />\n佢答唔係， 班本土派即刻瘋狂屌佢奶共， 無腰骨， 為五斗米折腰。 票王即刻變過街老鼠。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n至於泛民？ 而家仲妄想講乜撚野關鍵議席？<br />\n呢d就係無總辭， 攪唔成廣場立憲既後果。"},{"pid":"b0a0f960d1be64746fb2ba773f5641c5a1a22a93","tid":920244,"uid":72621,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T00:58:34.000Z","msg":"美國取消關係法又多一件證明"},{"pid":"bb87f40ed2ed2cf96e42ee9f63d20be3bb592687","tid":920244,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T05:01:31.000Z","msg":"-快點DQ"}]}